    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You cleave through foes that are packed together.</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - Melee - 1 Creature - Uses Equal to Proficiency Bonus/Long Rest</p><p>You use your normal &amp;reference[attack] action, but one of your attacks is replaced by Cleave. Make a melee weapon attack against one target creature and all creatures of your choice within 5 ft. of your target. You are still limited by your weapon's normal &amp;reference[reach]. You roll a single synchronous attack roll for all targets, dealing the same damage to each. </p><p></p><p><em>Cleave counts as an area of effect ability for the purposes of attacking swarms, and if targeting a creature with @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.PTAk4NGn6oIrRq1A]{Mirror Image} active, you target all images and the caster.</em></p>",
